item.description:
Sometimes you need the RDPW files when having for example remote apps listed in a central portal application integration. Here is a quick tip on how to download the Azure Virtual Desktop RDPW files for desktops and remote apps.
1. Log in using the AVD WebClient using the following URL: https://client.wvd.microsoft.com/arm/webclient/index.html 2. In the right corner click on the Settings wheel
3. Select in &ldquo;Resources Launch Method&rdquo; section for &ldquo;Download the rdp file&rdquo;
